Mastermind - Classic
Remember the classic Mastermind game from the Seventies? Now it's available for free in the
Apple App Store
and on
Google play
.
Mastermind - Classic is available in 13 languages.
Mastermind is a code-breaking game. You play against the computer and have ten tries to guess a hidden color code. After each try, you get a hint to see how many colors you have correct.
Read more about the game here
.
Beware. This game is highly addictive.
